post.description:
This endpoint assigns to a vehicle one job with one task using enforce path and forcing the route path to use a route template or several, so the driver when doing the task can follow a specific route path.
            
            
Conditions:
* "jobId" exists in the user account with only one task;
* vehicle is configured with WFM and can receive enforce paths;
* route templates exists in the user account;
* user has jobs permission and send route to a vehicle permission;
            
            
E.g.:
            
* Vehicle XX-00-ZZ, location Lisbon
* Job 0001 Task 1: Pickup goods at Paris - France
            
| Route template id | Route template name |
|:-----------------:|:-------------------:|
| 01 | Badajoz - Madrid |
