| 03 | IrÃºn - Coignieres |
            
* The vehicle XX-00-ZZ receives the job 0001 with only one route path: Badajoz - Madrid - IrÃºn - Coignieres - Paris
* The last step is generated by connecting the route template 03: IrÃºn - Coignieres to the job/task destination: Paris - France
            
            
* NOTE 1: if the end of a route template and the begging of the next route template is not the same spot(a place), route path should connect these 2 points, using the same method for the last step added to the route path;
* NOTE 2: the route templates are received in the order of execution, first template connects to second template,..., last template received connects to the task where-&gt;location;

