get.description:
The method returns the CANBus records for a daily period defined by the provided date. The period will be 00:00:00 UTC to 23:59:59 UTC. The values returned per record are:
* licensePlate: license plate of the vehicle as defined in Frotcom;
* totalFuelUsed: total fuel consumed by the vehicle since it left the factory, measured in liters;
* odometer: vehicle odometer;
* engineHours: total engine hours since vehicle left the factory;
* date: timestamp of the record
